            <title>[HBASE-8046] Update or delete HBaseConfTool</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8046</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HBaseConfTool looks like it could be handy for people who don&apos;t feel comfortable digging into ruby/shell and don&apos;t have a configuration manager like CM/Ambari.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If no one uses it, we should just delete it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If we want to keep it around, clean it up to use the Tool interface, GenericOptionParser, etc; change the interface audience to Public, maybe add support for wild-card matching, or at least dumping the entire config; document it in the book.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
